{"tid":652390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[忽發奇想]睇完地厚天高對首插曲有感","createTime":"2018-05-03T21:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T21:26:29.000Z","uid":136156,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37620433bc48fb6271025339be28a59f23ddb4d9","tid":652390,"uid":136156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T21:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=prwRv2boaj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DprwRv2boaj4&d=%2BPYKQrzF%2B8QwpqPDvRT4SS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=35628396\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=prwRv2boaj4</a><br />\n<br />\n最後梁天琦自彈自唱十八固然令人深刻<br />\n但其實最令人無奈係播羅大佑呢首東方之珠個陣<br />\n<br />\n背境交替播777宣誓同反釋法遊行 電視慶祝淪陷晚會同萬家燈火既香港<br />\n浮現係電視既歌舞昇平 同眾負所望既本土派衰落既現實作對比<br />\n象徵著近幾年好多人對香港現況既無力感 睇到呢幕差啲喊撚左出黎 <br />\n<br />\n講返首歌 其實係幾好聽同象徵到香港 但歌詞就出撚左事 <br />\n例如我永遠不變黃色的臉 讓海風吹拂了五千年之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似溏衣毒藥咁蠶食香港人既身份<br />\n<br />\n所以突然有個好左膠既idea 就係將呢首歌填上代表本土既歌詞<br />\n唔知有冇人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求集思廣益"},{"pid":"dfb66843eb02fcd57616b328dddcac6bf4017449","tid":652390,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T21:26:29.000Z","msg":"「小河灣灣向南流 流到香江去看一看」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以全年365日都有中國自由行旅客想黎香港看一看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}